high_descs: Walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the small end table in between the two beds.
Pick up the watch that is to the right of the credit card on the end table in front of you.

Turn around and walk out from in between the two beds, then turn left and walk across the room, then turn left and start walking to the door, turn right and walk over to the right side of the wooden desk.
Place the watch in the closest grey bowl on the desk.
Pick up the grey bowl with the watch in it.
Turn left and walk over to the black bin, then turn right and walk around the partition to the end table in between the two beds.
Put the grey bow with the watch in it onto the end table to the left of the pen.
anns.task_desc: Put a grey bowl with a watch in it on the end table.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the bedside table between beds.
Pick up the watch from the bedside table.
Turn around, walk past the bed, turn left and left again, then right and follow the desk to the right.
Set the watch in the bowl on the desk.
Pick up the bowl and watch from the desk.
Follow the same path back to the bedside table.
Set the watch and bowl on the bedside table.
anns.task_desc: Put the watch in the bowl and put it away on the bedside table.

high_descs: go to your left in between the two beds to the end table
pick up the wrist watch
turn around go back the the end of the beds then go around the farthest bed
continue to your right to the desk that is against the wall next to the door
face the desk and put the watch in the bowl at the end of the desk
pick up the bowl with the watch in it carry it back to the end table between the two beds
place the bowl and watch on the end table on the left side
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a watch in it on an end table between two beds
